title: Rainessa ASMR
description:
ヽ(*＾ω＾*)ﾉ Welcome Friend!

Thank you so much for stopping by!  

I hope you find this channel to be a spot of relaxation, calm & peace.

My goal is to share creativity, positivity & love to help you sleep comfortably & soundly!

Good night & sweet dreams, my friend!!!!! ♥♥♥

What is ASMR?
ASMR stands for autonomous sensory meridian response which is a biological reaction that some people may experience when they hear, see or feel certain satisfying triggers such as whispering, tapping, brushing or typing. It is best know for causing tingly sensations, relaxation and comfortable feelings.

Because of this, many people use ASMR as a way to help relax and sooth their mind and bodies before falling asleep. It can be used for meditation, sound therapy and is a natural sleep aid. I watch ASMR every night to fall asleep - and several times throughout the day as a part of my self care practice to keep my body, mind & spirit healthy and balanced! I love it!!!

description:
Hey friend! Welcome to my main channel Ozley ASMR (my only other channel is Ozley ASMR Shorts).  I am SO happy you decided to stop by! Grab your headphones for the full binaural experience, curl up with a cozy blanket, and stay awhile.

If you are new to ASMR, it stands for Autonomous Sensory Meridian Response, and it's a delightful tingly sensation some people get when experiencing certain sounds or visuals (tapping, rain, whispering, hand movements, just to name a few). Even if you don't experience "the tingles" these videos are perfect for relaxing, studying, and falling asleep. 

Have a browse through my collection of videos and don't forget to say hi before you go!

title: FrivolousFox ASMR
description:
Howdy ho hi B) I'm Frivvi. or Lauren. But Frivvi sounds cooler so we'll go with that. Welcome :')

After losing the love of my life due to a car accident (its complicated), I became depressed & reclusive. This channel served as an outlet for me to be *me.* To learn, grow, connect, & heal. For me, ASMR isn't just about tingles or relaxation. It's about feeling good. Smiling. Laughing. Connecting. Feeling a part of something bigger, but something REAL. I'm not the most professional or technically-polished ASMRtist, but that's okay! I think. Probably not. But if you extend a bit of patience, I'll prove that this channel & community is worth it. Or can be. Just gO WITH IT OK

Frivolous means light-hearted. Foxes are cool. ASMR isn't a medical alternative, but it's helped me in a way no therapist could. I whisper, I ramble, I tap, I kiss, I nom, I sing, I mess up, I giggle. I would LOVE for you to join me on this journey of self-acceptance, love, *MOUTH SOUNDS*, tingles & smiles.

AFFILIATE LINKS
E-Win Racing: https://bit.ly/3vfVQYl & 20% off promo code "theASMRnerd"
Into The AM: https://bit.ly/ASMRnerdINTOTHEAM

WHAT IS ASMR?
My videos are designed to trigger a relaxing feeling called ASMR (Autonomous Sensory Meridian Response). ASMR is a particular sensation that some people experience when they hear quiet sounds like whispering and soft speaking or watch certain actions like slow hand motions. ASMR is often described as a pleasant tingling on the head and neck, accompanied by a feeling of deep calm and mild euphoria. Many people watch ASMR videos to relax and manage anxiety, stress, or insomnia. To learn more about ASMR, check out https://asmruniversity.com/about-asmr/what-is-asmr.

title: asmr zeitgeist
description:
ASMR Zeitgeist provides you with high-quality ASMR video content to help you sleep and relax. Tingles guaranteed! ;D

ASMR (АСМР, 音フェチ) stands for Autonomous Sensory Meridian Response and describes a pleasurable tingling sensation on the scalp or spine triggered by various stimuli.

These triggers might be sounds like soft whispering, crinkly plastic, tapping or scratching different materials and many more. 

The science behind this euphoric experience has to be further explored. Some reliable studies already suggest that it can be a powerful method to help people reduce depression, anxiety or insomnia. 

This YouTube channel is dedicated to the zeitgeist of ASMR. My goal is to offer all the popular triggers in optimal sound quality and to break new grounds with an open mind and creativity. I want you to have the best possible ASMR!

If you are seeking for some tingling relaxation, subscribe and hit the notification bell! :)

title: ASMR & R
description:
こんにちは✨

リコです。


動画を見て頂きありがとうございます😃

ASMR とは「人が聴覚や視覚への刺激によって感じる、心地良い、脳がゾワゾワするといった反応・感覚」を指すもの。

というように一般的に表現されています。


もし貴方が

👉🏻お仕事や勉強、家事、育児などで疲れ気味

👉🏻色々あって精神的に弱ってる

👉🏻病気で辛い

👉🏻ここ最近不眠続き

などで困っているとしたら、、


私はそんな貴方に映像を通して少しでも解放された心地よい時間をお届けできたらという思いを込め丁寧にASMR 動画を制作し投稿してます🕊


ASMR チャンネルを開設を決めたきっかけは、自身の病気です。


私は2年近く前から難治療の病気になり、仕事と身体の自由を奪われて外出がままならなくなり、一時は絶望的な状態になっていました。


元々切り替えが早い性格なところもあり、こんな私でもとにかく出来る事を見つけて1日でも早く新しい事をスタートしなくては、精神的にとても良くないと思っていた頃、たまたま見つけた動画がASMRでした 👂🏻


体力のない私にエネルギーをたくさん必要としない囁き声で話すasmrは今の私にもできるかもと思いスタートしてみました。


今ではASMR にすっかりはまり、動画作成が楽しくて、何より見てくれる方が「眠れた」「リラックスできた」など言ってもらえる事が嬉しくてたまりません。そして視聴者の方から沢山のエネルギーを頂き感謝しています☺️

頂いたエネルギーを動画を通し循環していきたいです。



それでは貴方が心地よく感じてもらえる動画はどんなものなのか？をひたすら追求しながら、今後も沢山動画を投稿していきます✨


チャンネル登録、いいね、コメント大歓迎です❤️❤️❤️


どうぞよろしくお願いします❤️

より動画の質を上げるために欲しい物が沢山あります＾＾
もしプレゼントしても良いよって方がいらしたら倒れてしまいそうなくらい嬉しいです❤️

title: ASMR Jeremiah
description:
Welcome to my corner of the ASMR universe. 

Tingles, relaxation, connection, and deep, deep sleep. 

ASMR stands for autonomous sensory meridian response. It's the tingly sensation people get when they hear certain sounds. 

I've had trouble sleeping for the past several years and I want to help others get the deep sleep they deserve. 

Not every person gets the "tingles", but even non-tinglers can get a deep sense of relaxation and calm as they drift into peaceful slumber. 

Put on your headphones or earbuds to enjoy the 3D binaural soundscape, take a deep breath, and relax with me as we explore this amazing sensory world. 

With Warmth and Affection,
ASMR Jeremiah

title: JayLynn ASMR
description:
I am a Canadian ASMRtist who has been watching ASMR on a daily basis since 2014, but has experienced ASMR since I was a young child. I decided to create a YouTube channel to help others the way ASMR has helped me. 

ASMR has helped me through stress, inability to fall asleep, anxiety, panic, and depression. I know I cannot cure these for you, but my hope is that I can at the very least help you relax and make your day a little better. 

The main purpose of this channel is to relax you, and create a calming environment. It is a place of positivity, and to feel safe. Relax, and happy drifting, everyone!

I prefer fast ASMR triggers, so my pace is generally fast and focus mainly on tapping and scratching! :)

title: Auralia ASMR
description:
ASMR - DEINE EINSCHLAFHILFE 

Willkommen auf ASMR Auralia, deinem Kanal für Entspannung!
Mach’s dir bequem, lehn dich zurück und genieße die meditativen ASMR basierenden Sounds. Dieses Deepsonic Hörvergnügen soll dir dabei helfen aus dem stressigen Alltag auszubrechen und dich in eine entspannte Traumwelt gleiten zu lassen…

Kontakt: auralia@njoy.at

🎧 ASMR - Autonomous Sensory Meridian Response 🎧
Ein sanftes Kribbeln am Kopf, welches sich dann im Nacken und schließlich über die Wirbelsäule im ganzen Körper ausbreitet. Ja so könnte man den ASMR-Genuss für Unwissende beschreiben.  Die Kurzform ASMR steht für "Autonomous Sensory Meridian Response" und bezeichnet eine Entspannungsmethode, bei dem das Gehirn wohltuend auf bestimmte Geräusche oder Stimmen reagiert. Durch diese verschieden Trigger werden angenehme Gefühle (sogenannte Tingles) ausgelöst, welche ein sanftes Kribbeln, Gänsehaut und ganzheitliche Entspannung liefern. 

Deine Auralia ✨

title: Hatomugi ASMR
description:
どうも、はとむぎです！
このチャンネルでは、主に「ASMR動画」を投稿しています。

◆ASMRとは、Autonomous Sensory Meridian Responseの略称で、大まかに意訳すると、人が聴覚や視覚への刺激によって感じる「状態・感覚」のことを言います。

「状態・感覚」には、物理的なものと、心理的なものの2種類あります。
映像や音声から受ける「刺激」から、首や背骨、頭の中や体全体がぞくぞくすることが物理的な感覚で、幸福感や安らぎ、落ち着き、気持ちの良い眠気などを感じるのが心理的な感覚です。

ASMRの「刺激」を受ける一般的なタイプは、
・視覚（見て）
・聴覚（聞いて）
・触覚（触って）
の３つです。

※)
視覚の例：目を見つめられる、ゆっくりとした手の動きなど
触覚の例：軽いタッチやマッサージ、頭を触れるなど
聴覚の例：人の声(囁き、ゆっくりした声、優しい声)や口の音(咀嚼、呼吸)、物体(タッピング、スクラッチング、操作音、なでる)など様々…

「刺激」を得る場所として、私のチャンネルの動画のような電子の中、もしくは人の声や動作、物の音など実生活の中でも感じることがあります。
直接得る刺激以外でも、想像したり瞑想したり、知らぬ間にASMRが引き起こされる場合もあります。

ASMRの刺激と、引き起こされる感覚は個人間で大きく異なります。
全体に共通して言えるのは、ASMRは多種多様なきっかけにより引き起こされた「深いリラックス状態」であるということ。

音や映像の好み、感じ方は人それぞれですので、ASMRの動画は、好き嫌いが極端に分かれるジャンルかもしれません。
私の動画以外にも、ASMRを引き起こすきっかけになる映像や音声がたくさんありますので、是非ご自身の好きな動画を探してみてくださいね。

※無断転載はご遠慮願います。

title: PARIS ASMR
description:
My name is Flo. I live in Paris. I have always enjoyed the ASMR. My first memories go back to my childhood. ASMR is a gentle feeling of warmth and relaxation located in the skull. This feeling helps me relax and connect to the present moment. On my channel, I want to take care of you and trigger your ASMR with relaxing sounds.  

Je m'appelle Flo et je vis à Paris. J'ai toujours été sensible à l'ASMR. Mes premiers souvenirs remontent à la petite enfance. L'ASMR est une sensation de douce chaleur, d'ondes vibratoires au niveau du crâne. Cette sensation est tellement forte qu'elle me fige, elle me statufie, elle me met littéralement en veille. Je crois que mes premiers souvenirs remontent à l'âge de 5 ou 6 ans quand mes parents m'emmenaient chez le coiffeur. C'est aussi dans les bibliothèques et les librairies que cette sensation a été encore plus intense. J'ai ressenti l'irrépressible envie de donner à mon tour de l'ASMR parce que j'aime tant prendre soin des autres...

title: Sezgin,ce ASMR
description:
Merhabalar adım sezgin 38 yaşındayım youtube de  ASMR videolarımı kaçırmamak için kanalıma abone olmayı unutmayın ! 
ASMR NEDİR? ASMR’ın Türkçe karşılığı en basit ifade ile “iç gıdıklanması” olarak tanımlanabilir. Doktorlar tarafından yapılan bilimsel tanımlaması ise “sürüngen beyin durumu” olarak ifade edilmektedir. ASMR olgusu beyinin duyduğu bazı seslerin (düşük desibel gücüne sahip sesler) beyinde uyandırdığı işitme temeline dayanan bir histir. “Tingle” yani beyin karıncalanması hissi, birçok ses ile meydana gelebilir. Bunlara tırnak tıkırdatması, fısıltı, klavye sesleri, kağıt sesleri örnek olarak verilebilir. 
Asmr, uyku problemleri çeken insanlarda olumlu sonuçlar verebilen, zihni rahatlatan ve beyin orgazmı olarak da bilinen bir terimdir. Rahat uyku, uyku meditasyonu, uyku telkini, rahatlatıcı sesler, uyku getirici videolar, zihin rahatlatıcı telkinleri bu kanalda bulabilirsiniz.

title: Chiara ASMR
description:
❤ Sono Chiara, ho 28 anni e per lavoro fra le altre cose sussurro a dei microfoni.
Sono laureata in Chimica e Tecnologia Farmaceutiche, ma per ora la mia passione è anche il mio lavoro.
Ho scritto "Il potere di un sussurro", il primo libro sull'ASMR in Italia, in cui parlo a 360° dell'argomento e scoprirai le basi scientifiche dell'ASMR, oltre che a tutti i segreti e consigli per gestire un canale ASMR al meglio e come ha influenzato la mia vita.
L' ASMR è una sensazione di brividini rilassanti sul corpo provocata da stimoli uditivi e visivi. E' una coccola e un aiuto per combattere insonnia e stress.

O QUE É ASMR ? 

ASMR é uma sigla para Autonomous Sensory Meridian Response, que significa Resposta Sensorial Meridiana Autônoma. Esse termo é usado para descrever a sensação agradável causada por alguma experiência sensorial, que pode ser desencadeada por sons como sussurros ou escovação, e estímulos visuais como pintura ou desenho.

O propósito do ASMR é relaxar as pessoas, proporcionando ao espectador um formigamento relaxante na parte de trás da cabeça ou da coluna.

title: HunniBee ASMR
description:
Hello :)
This is an ASMR channel, which hopefully helps you either fall asleep or just feel relaxed ^__^
ASMR stands for autonomous sensory meridian response which can feel like a tingling sensation on the skin that usually starts at the scalp and moves down to the back of the neck and upper spine. (Got that definition from wikipedia lol it's not my own). But if you've ever had someone play with your hair or draw on your back, which I'm sure you have, you would have experienced this feeling!! title: ASMR Lá Nas Alturas
description:
Namastê! Eu sou Ana Gutierrez, te desejo boas vindas ao Lá Nas Alturas! Eu acredito no ASMR como ferramenta terapêutica para o bem-estar holístico, autoconhecimento e prática meditativa, por isso, integro a esse método de relaxamento os conhecimentos de meus estudos e experiências nesta área.

Sou terapeuta, com especialização em Bem-Estar pela PUC-RS e em Saúde Integrativa pela Universidade de Minnesota (EUA). Possuo certificação em Aconselhamento de Bem-Estar Existencial pela Universidade de KU Leuven (Bélgica) e formação em mais de 10 técnicas com abordagem holística.

ASMR: sigla para Resposta Sensorial Autônoma do Meridiano. Termo que descreve a agradável sensação de formigamento geralmente sentida na região do couro cabeludo em resposta a estímulos visuais, auditivos e cognitivos. São vídeos com voz suave, sussurros, sons de objetos ou movimentos, utilizados para relaxamento e para indução ao sono. Procure um ambiente tranquilo e utilize fones de ouvido para melhor resultado.

title: Thildou ASMR
description:
Coucou toi, 

Si tu lis cette description, c'est que tu es arrivé sur ma chaîne ASMR, un lieu où je fais de mon mieux pour faire du bien à tes petites oreilles. 👂🏻

Alors alors, ta présence ici veut dire que soit tu es un amateur d'ASMR et tu es donc au bon endroit, soit que tu es curieux ce qui est tout à ton honneur, soit que tu t'es perdu, auquel cas ne fais pas demi tour tu pourrais faire de jolies découvertes !😇

ASMR par ci, ASMR par là, mais qu'est-ce que c'est au fait l'ASMR?🤷🏻‍♀️
L'ASMR c'est tout simple, c'est la sensation déclenchée par une personne qui fait de petits sons pour te faire passer un moment agréable. L'ASMR est une méthode qui permet aux gens de se détendre, de se relaxer, d'évacuer le stress parfois même de s'endormir !(oui je t'assure) 🌙
Il y a plusieurs types de sons en ASMR, vraiment beaucoup de sons, et j'essaierai à travers mes vidéos de t'en faire découvrir un maximum.

J’espère que tu passeras de chouettes moments ici, en ma compagnie!

Thildou ❤️

title: asmr soupe
description:
몰입과 평온함이 가득한 일상이 될 수 있도록 - Finding Flow & Tranquility

『삶을 고양시키고 훌륭하게 가꾸어주는 것은 단순히 행복하다는 불확실한 감정이 아니라, 깊이 빠져드는 몰입이다.』

Flow란, 미하이 칙센트미하이의 저서에 등장한 단어로 자신에 대한 의식이 사라질 정도로 어떤 일에 깊이 몰입하는 것을 뜻합니다. 
Tranquility는 걱정 근심 없는 고요하고 평온한 상태를 말하는 것으로, 단순한 휴식을 넘어선 명상의 느낌에 가깝다 할 수 있겠네요. 

여러분들의 일상에 몰입과 평온함이 가득할 수 있도록, 늘 곁에서 작은 힘이 되는 수프이고 싶습니다. :)

수프soupe라는 이름은 오래 전에 1인 출판사를 시작하며 지은 브랜드 이름입니다. 한 모금 마시는 것만으로도 몸과 마음이 따뜻하고 포근해 지는 '수프'같은 콘텐츠를 만들어 나가고 싶어요.


■비즈니스 문의, 응원의 편지, 의견 보내 주실 분들은 :
neverend@gmail.com

■더 좋은 컨텐츠를 위해 후원해 주실 분들은 :
https://toon.at/donate/asmrsoupe

◆대부분의 영상은 입체 음향(Binaural Sounds)으로 제작되고 있으므로 이어폰을 착용하시면 소리를 더 실감나게 감상하실 수 있습니다!

FAQ

● 유튜브에 배경음 등으로 활용이 가능한가요?
재사용은 어렵습니다. 무단으로 사용할 경우 유료 라이센스로 구입한 소스들이 저작권 위반으로 문제가 되니 주의해 주세요!

● 소리와 사진은 전부 직접 만들고 찍은 건가요?
직접 제작한 것과 저작권 없는 것들, 라이센스를 구입한 자료를 섞어 사용해요.

● 음향 관련 일을 하고 있나요?
사운드에 대한 지식이 조금 있을 뿐 전문가는 아니고요, 스스로 연구하고 배워가며 제작하고 있어요.

● 저작권에 문제는 없나요?
원작의 영상, 효과음, 이미지를 쓰지 않습니다. 원작의 이미지에 누가 되지 않고 시너지를 낼 수 있는 방향으로 콘텐츠를 제작하고 있어요.

title: benio店長 / ASMR屋さん
description:
いらっしゃいませ、ASMR屋さんへようこそ！
週1~2本・水曜or土曜に動画投稿してます🎞

*ASMR屋さんは「ASMRのバラエティ番組」のような
見ても聞いても楽しい癒しのお店を目指しています🌙

*さまざまなASMRを取り扱っておりますので
あなた好みの「ASMR」を見つけてみてね😴

🗝 「ASMR」とは…
Autonomous Sensory Meridian Response＝自律感覚絶頂反応。聴覚・視覚へ刺激を与え、脳に鳥肌が立つようなゾクゾクした感覚、心地よく眠気を誘う感覚などのこと。

🗝 ｢ASMR｣を楽しむには…
トリガー(trigger)とは、ASMRを感じるためのキッカケの事。囁き声、物を触る音、ゆっくりとした手の仕草、などがトリガーの一種です。人それぞれ独自の感覚・好みのトリガーがあり、場合によっては快感を覚える人・不快感を覚える人もいます。

title: Flüsterliebe ASMR
description:
Hallo Welt, hey du! 🌍 
ASMR - Was bitte ist das?! 😱... 
Genau dieser Gedanke kam mir auch, als ich das erste Mal von Flüstervideos und Triggern die Tingles auslösen gehört habe.
Doch ein kleiner Teil von mir war neugierig, wollte unbedingt die Begeisterung für diese Videos verstehen und das 'Gehirnkribbeln' selber fühlen. Kurzum habe ich mir ein paar ASMRtist's angeschaut, mich zunehmend drauf eingelassen und festgestellt, dass ASMR (Autonomes Sensor Meridian Response) eine unfassbar großartige Möglichkeit zu entspannen, runterzukommen und vom Alltag abzuschalten. Tja, dass Thema hat mich also richtig angefixt. 
Geht's dir genauso? Dann setze deine Kopfhörer auf und abonniere meinen Kanal... 🎧
Hier findest du ASMR Videos auf deutsch.
Bis bald, 
deine Flüsterliebe ✨

P.S. Neue Videos gibt es immer Mittwochs. 🎉

#asmrdeutsch #asmr #Kopfkribbeln

description:
Ambience Heaven is an ASMR & Soundscapes channel born to bring you moments of calm and peace. Nowadays stressful life doesn't allow much time for ourselves, neither permits a time of peaceful silence in our mind. Ambience Heaven is here to bring a moment of slow life, to create a space for blissful calm. These ambiences and soundscapes allow us to create and evolve and are the perfect environment to read, study, meditate, or for sewing, painting, or whatever you may like to do in your leisure time.  With the help of animated images and pictures made by artists or by ourselves and sound captions, we create an atmosphere for you to enjoy. Come, we will take you by the hand to a world of relaxation and stillness.

title: ASMR Pépite
description:
Salut moi c'est Pépite,

Bienvenue sur ma chaine ASMR, je suis la pour t'aider a te relaxé, apaisé ton cœur et si j'y arrive t'aidé a t'endormir.

J'espère que mes vidéos te feront du bien, ici il y a juste de l'amour et de la bienveillance.

En espérant que tu puisse trouver ton bonheur sur cette chaine #ASMR.

Qu'est ce que l'ASMR ?
L'ASMR est une technique de relaxation composée de son étrange et de parole chuchotées qui déclenche un bien-être intense  accompagné de petit frisson qui peut aider a mieux dormir, a diminuer le stress et a se détendre après une longue journée difficile. 
    
J.❤

✨ C ' E S T   Q U O I   L ' A S M R ?  
ASMR (meaning Autonomous sensory meridian response) est un sigle qui décrit une sensation distincte et agréable de picotements ou frissons au niveau du crâne, du cuir chevelu ou des zones périphériques du corps, en réponse à un stimulus visuel, auditif, olfactif ou cognitif. 
En gros, c'est de la relaxation par le son !

title: LullingLisa ASMR
description:
Lulling you into a state of relaxation, sleep, or entertainment through ASMR.

Hi I'm Lisa, welcome to my ASMR channel. I'm so happy that you've found me :)
I upload every Mon, Wed, & Fri! 

What is ASMR? "ASMR stands for 'autonomous sensory meridian response'. People describe a deeply relaxing sensation with tingling in the scalp as a result of a certain stimulus—often a gentle sound. Some say the feeling cascades down their spine to their limbs". ASMR is triggered by things such as whispering, softly speaking, tapping, personal attention, accents, and other various triggers. I personally enjoy ASMR as entertainment, for relaxation, to help with sleep, and also to manage stress. Many people also use ASMR for comfort, and to feel less alone as well, which is a wonderful feeling of community and belonging. I hope you all feel welcome here, and I hope to lull you into a state of relaxation, entertainment, or maybe even sleep through my ASMR videos.

Love, Lisa (LullingLisa ASMR)

title: ASMR Jeremiah
description:
Welcome to my corner of the ASMR universe. 

Tingles, relaxation, connection, and deep, deep sleep. 

ASMR stands for autonomous sensory meridian response. It's the tingly sensation people get when they hear certain sounds. 

I've had trouble sleeping for the past several years and I want to help others get the deep sleep they deserve. 

Not every person gets the "tingles", but even non-tinglers can get a deep sense of relaxation and calm as they drift into peaceful slumber. 

Put on your headphones or earbuds to enjoy the 3D binaural soundscape, take a deep breath, and relax with me as we explore this amazing sensory world. 

With Warmth and Affection,
ASMR Jeremiah

title: DoDa AsMr🎧😴
description:
أشخاص يهمسون إليك أمام الكاميرا. فالهمس أهم ثيمات «إيسمار»، وهو موجود في كل المقاطع على اختلافها. قد يقترن هذا الهمس بحركات تشبه الطبطبة أو التربيت على كتفك أو المسح على شعرك، مع قدر من التواصل البصري يعطيك إحساسًا بالاهتمام الشخصي.

أشخاص يكرمشون/يعفسون أغلفة بلاستيكية، أو ينقرون بأظافرهم على سطح بلاستيكي أو يستعرضون طرقًا لطي المناشف. وربما تشاهد خطاطًا يمارس الكتابة في محاولة لتطويع محفزات سمعية وبصرية.

أشخاص يمثلون أدوارًا مثل طبيب يفحصك أو كوافير يقص شعرك أو موظف يستقبلك في الفندق، في محاولة لإعطاء المتلقي اهتمامًا شخصيًّا مُركَّزًا.

لكن محتوى «إيه إس إم آر» متنوع ويتوسع باستمرار، حتى إنه توجد مقاطع مخصصة للأطفال، تساعدهم على النوم. ويستخدم صانعو محتوى «إيه إس إم آر» الجيد ميكروفونات ثلاثية الأبعاد، لالتقاط صوت أنفاسهم وأنعم الأصوات وأرقها
DoDa ASMR 🎧❤️

title: ASMR TOP No1
description:
Привет,Вы на канале ASMR TOP1,меня зовут Татьяна 
Здесь я делаю видео для вашего сна и расслабления.
Хочу,чтобы вы были более здоровыми и спокойными - и тогда у вас все будет получаться ,все будет хорошо 💜
АСМР видео - что это такое и с чем их едят?
В наше время на многих популярных видеохостингах, появились  ASMR видео, способные пощекотать ваш мозг, вызвать мурашки на вашем теле и просто дать возможность испытать эстетическое удовольствие от увиденного и услышанного.
Ничего пошлого.просто расслабьтесь и отдыхайте )
Определение из Википедии:
«Автономная сенсорная меридиональная реакция (АСМР)— это неологизм, обозначающий феномен восприятия, характеризующийся приятным ощущением покалывания в затылке, распространяющегося в виде мурашек по коже шеи и спине к конечностям. Вызывают АСМР-ощущения звуковые, зрительные, тактильные или когнитивные стимулы.»

Hello there!

Welcome to my ASMR eating sounds channel where I enjoy a variety of delicious vegan foods for your relaxation and viewing pleasure :) 

All meals are 100% plant-based. And I don't always finish my food...

Thank you so much for watching!

What is ASMR? Autonomous Sensory Meridian Response (ASMR) is a physical and pleasurable reaction to certain acoustic, visual and/or tactile stimuli. These soothing stimuli can evoke relaxation, sleepiness, body tingling, stress relief, euphoria, comfort, and a sense of calm in those who experience ASMR. Common triggers include repetitive sounds, personal attention, soft touch, whispering and hand movements.

title: AftynRose ASMR
description: Hi there! My name is Aftyn and thank you for visiting my channel! I make videos designed to help you relax, feel happy, or trigger what we call tingles throughout your body. ASMR stands for autonomous sensory meridian response and refers to a tingly, static like sensation due to the use of sounds and sometimes visuals- although I believe the visual trigger is referred to as AVRIC. In my videos I like to combine the two in hopes of creating a comforting experience for you. I try to be as open and myself as possible in the videos and I hope that you enjoy my personality, and the love that I wish to give. It is my dream to open your mind up to a new form of relaxation and to help you feel as loved and at ease with the current moment as possible. Anxiety, depression, and loneliness are some of the worst feelings to cope with and my hope with ASMR is to make those long lonely nights a bit easier on you. I hope you find something here for you and thanks again for checking out my channel!

Hi everyone, and welcome to my channel, eunoia corinne asmr! I really hope that you can find comfort, relaxation, and safety in my videos as that’s what I turn to ASMR for ♥️

I first got into ASMR in 2016, and now watch it every night before I go to sleep, as well as occasionally watching it as background for studying/working. 

I’ve always played around with the idea of starting my own channel, but was always worried about the idea of showing my face. Because of my ✨insecurities and low self esteem✨, I’ve decided to start this channel with no intentions of showing my face, and I hope this can be understood 💓

I’m so excited to go on this journey and I’m so happy that you’re a part of it - even just by reading this, you’ve contributed greatly and I can only hope to return the favour through my videos ❤️

ASMR bezeichnet das Gefühl eines Kribbelns im Körper (englisch „tingle“) ausgelöst durch akustische, visuelle und taktile Sinnesreize (sogenannte „trigger“).

title: ohr.g. asmr
description:
Oh nein!!
Oh ja: Noch ein ASMR-Kanal.Ich weiß: Es gibt schon eine unüberschaubare Auswahl an ASMR-Videos.Ich bediene mich seit ca 2 Jahren an diesem Fundus von Entspannungsvideos und möchte sie nicht missen. Allerdings ist mir eine Entwicklung aufgefallen, die mich sehr ratlos macht und die meinen Präferenzen -was ASMR-Videos betrifft- genau entgegen verläuft: Immer mehr Roleplays, Overdupping, layered Sounds usw. Viele Videos ähneln mittlerweile eher Produktbeschreibungen, in denen dann auch mal "getappt" oder "gecrinkelt" wird. Außerdem verlieren die Videos je perfekter sie gemacht sind ihre Wirkung auf mich. Wie gesagt, das gilt für mich so, andere mögen es anders empfinden. Aber wenn ich eines gelernt habe im Leben: Man ist nie allein...immer gibt es Menschen, die ähnlich fühlen wie man selbst. Für diese Menschen ist dieser Kanal gedacht (natürlich auch für alle anderen,die vielleicht ein wenig Spaß/Entspannung finden beim Betrachten bzw Hören).

title: Nanas ASMR
description:
Hello it's me Nana and welcome to my relaxing bubble of ASMR. 

Aloha, Namaste, ich bin Nana und willkommen auf meinem ASMR Kanal. Ich hoffe das ich dich mit meinen Inhalten entspannen kann. Ich habe lange überlegt ob ich solch einen Kanal starten soll oder nicht. Schließlich ist es etwas intimes und es gibt leider noch sehr viele Menschen die entweder nichts damit anfangen können, es in eine bestimmte Schublade stecken, oder diese Art von Videos sehr seltsam finden. Wie man hier sehen kann ist es wohl soweit und ich starte meinen Kanal! Nein, ich springe nicht auf den neuen Hype ASMR Zug auf, ich erlebe das schon seit meiner Kindheit. Damals konnte natürlich noch kein Mensch was mit dem Begriff ASMR anfangen. Ich freue mich teil dieser Community zu sein und bin sehr gespannt auf die kommende Zeit.

title: ZYLIARA ASMR
description:
Hi!
My name is Zy-Liara :)

This channel is all about ASMR. What is that, you ask?

ASMR (АСМР, 音フェチ) stands for Autonomous Sensory Meridian Response
and describes a pleasurable tingling sensation on the scalp or spine triggered by various stimuli.

These triggers might be sounds like soft whispering, crinkly plastic, tapping or scratching different materials and many more.
I mostly do rolelplays in different languages and incorporate those sounds in these first person videos.

The science behind the ASMR experience has to be further explored.
Some reliable studies already suggest that it can be a useful method to help people reduce depression, anxiety and insomnia.

Let's relax and enjoy this world of sounds.

Love,
Zy

title: Jimち ASMR
description:
Sometimes-weird 'inuntentional' ASMR and FPC videos to help you relax, unwind, and sleep. Often miswritten as Jim 5.

ASMR Community Guidelines: jimchicommunity.carrd.co

🎙 What is ASMR? 🎧

ASMR (autonomous sensory meridian response) is synaesthesia of the soul. It’s a relaxing feeling, it’s a tingling down the spine, or it’s simply a sleep aid. Whether it’s being ‘held’ by someone you have confidence in, or ‘looked after’ by someone with authority, or just feeling ‘safe’ with someone you trust, it uses audio-visual triggers to enable you to let go of your worries.

📽 What is FPC? 🎞

FPC (first person cinema) takes all the relaxing elements of ASMR but has much more of a focus on immersion and the suspension of disbelief. It’s kinda like being the main character in your own short movie, with popular figures you know and love, or entirely created worlds – they are unique and relaxing experiences designed to transport you to different places, worlds, and times.

title: Clickmyworld ASMR
description:
Ciao, benvenut*!
Mi chiamo Fiorella e questo canale YouTube è dedicato al relax, precisamente all'ASMR.

🔸ASMR è un acronimo che sta per Autonomous Sensory Meridian Response, in italiano "Risposta Autonoma del Meridiano Sensoriale". 
🔸L'ASMR è una forma di profondo rilassamento indotto da qualcosa che si sente o si vede, spesso accompagnato da un formicolio che parte dal cervello per scendere poi lungo la spina dorsale ed estendersi a tutto il corpo.
🔸L'ASMR è anche definito orgasmo cerebrale con il neologismo inglese "braingasm". Gli inneschi che fanno scaturire queste piacevoli sensazioni si chiamano "triggers" e possono essere uditivi (quindi rumori, sussurri, suoni particolari) e visuali (ad esempio il dolce movimento delle mani).
🔸L'ASMR può aiutare a combattere insonnia, ansia, panico, negatività. Chiaramente non si sostituisce a un supporto psicoterapeutico.

E-mail: fiorellall88@gmail.com
Instagram: @fiore_sgrammaticando

title: Crescent Moon ASMR
description:
Hey! Welcome to my channel, I'm happy to see you here! This is an ASMR channel, so my goal is to relax you and make you feel confortable. I hope you'll enjoy the time spent here and feel free to come back whenever you want!

But...what is ASMR? 
ASMR is an acronym for “Autonomous Sensory Meridian Response", a physical sensation characterized by a pleasurable tingling that typically begins in the head and scalp, and often moves down the spine and through the limbs.
So, the sole purpose of ASMR videos is to relax and entertain the viewer. 
ASMR videos usually involve one or more of the following things:

• Gentle whispering 
• Relaxing hand movements 
• Smacking of the lips 
• Nail tapping/scratching on hard surfaces such as tables 
• Brushing sounds

title: Pit TheVoice ASMR
description:
Sono Pietro, in arte Pit. Sono un grande appassionato di musica e canto. Non a caso, ormai da tempo, la mia attività musicale è divenuta un vero e proprio lavoro.
Tuttavia, da qualche tempo a questa parte, mi sono avvicinato con estremo interesse al mondo del ASMR; avvicinamento che mi ha portato alla conseguente apertura di questo canale, dove avrete la possibilità di seguire dei video a tema, aventi l'obiettivo comune di farvi prendere sonno e rilassare.
Nella fattispecie il canale propone triggers uditivi e visivi, tra cui letture e racconti sussurrati o a voce bassa (whisper and soft spoken), gratto e strofinio leggero di superfici (light scratching), percussione leggera di oggetti (tapping) e rumori prodotti dalla bocca (mouth sounds).
I video verranno pubblicati ogni martedì e venerdì sera, alle ore 21.00.

Per eventuali collaborazioni (le accetto con piacere) potete scrivere a pit.thevoice.asmr@gmail.com

title: Al Lullaby ASMR
description:
Hi! I am a hair dryer collector and I think that hair dryer sound is the best white noise to sleep and relax. I upload a new hair dryer sound video every Monday. It is a visual ASMR video and a binaural recording as well, conceived to be a lullaby to sleep and relax.

I record my hairdryer sound videos wearing my white outfit with a pitch-black background. That setting and the slow movements I perform should trigger visual ASMR. You can appreciate the hair dryer sound itself, anyway: it is the perfect ASMR trigger!

I also upload a second video every Friday. It can be either a hair dryer sound collection, or a white noise video (such as a fan heater sound), or a nature sound video (such as a waterfall sound).

All my videos are ads-free and are binaural recording as well. Use headphones to better appreciate the binaural sound.

I hope my ASMR videos are a useful tool to relax and sleep. If you find them helpful, please subscribe to this channel, comment and like them!

Al Lullaby

title: Czas Po Deszczu ASMR
description:
Tworzę kontent o charakterze relaksacyjnym ASMR
ASMR - w wielkim skrócie jest to samoistna odpowiedź meridianów czuciowych, które na płaszczyźnie fizycznej ale również psychologicznej wywołują uczucie głębokiego błogostanu, bezpieczeństwa, odprężenia, wyciszenia lub bardzo często przyjemnego stanu senności. 
Wiele osób doświadczających zjawisko ASMR odczuwa na swoim ciele przyjemne ciarki lub mrowienie z tyłu głowy, w okolicach szyi czy też na plecach w strefie kręgosłupa. Nie jest to jednak wspólna cecha, występująca u wszystkich osób doświadczających ASMR, jak również nie wszyscy doświadczają zjawiska ASMR.

Zanim zaczniesz oglądać.
Jeżeli dopiero zaczynasz swoją przygodę z ASMR, zadbaj o to aby przez czas oglądanego filmu nikt Ci nie przeszkadzał, zajmij wygodną pozycję (usiądź w wygodnym fotelu lub połóż się) oraz dla lepszego efektu ASMR załóż słuchawki.

description:
Hi there! This is Mae!

I've been doing ASMR sessions for years now as a method of relaxing after long tiring days. Recently, my friend and I decided to start capturing it! I am very grateful to share these videos with you because we enjoy making them and they are very helpful in getting better sleep and relaxation.

title: TOUCH MUSEUM ASMR
description:
Touch Museum is an ASMR YouTube channel and immersive video installation by visual artist Julie Weitz. The project explores the experience of embodiment in the digital realm through the sensory phenomenon known as Autonomous Sensory Meridian Response. 

The exhibition originally premiered  at Young Projects Gallery in Los Angeles from November 2015- February 2016 and is currently on view at Archer School for Girls in Los Angeles, CA through December 16, 2016. 

For more information visit www.julieweitz.com.

description:
Cuando está triste o estresado, es posible que no pueda encontrar inmediatamente un lugar donde haya duchas, en Internet, hay muchos videos que graban el sonido de la lluvia y las olas.
O si eres más afortunado de vivir cerca de lugares como ríos, arroyos o el mar, o incluso donde solo tienes un lago muy pequeño, ve allí. Observar las ondas del agua, escuchar el suave sonido del agua que golpea la orilla también te ayudará a aliviar la sensación de aburrimiento y a reducir los pensamientos negativos que te atormentan. A partir de ahí, encontrará su mente tranquila, para mirar hacia atrás en lo que está sucediendo y, lo más importante, para mirar hacia atrás.

title: りさっぴ ASMR TV
description:
どうも、りさっぴです😊💖
このチャンネルでは、主に「ASMR動画」を投稿しています✨


私のプロフィールです
↓
住んでる所：愛媛県
年齢：秘密
家族：旦那、司（こども）、まる（ミニチュアダックスフンド）



◆ASMRとは、Autonomous Sensory Meridian Responseの略称で、大まかに意訳すると、人が聴覚や視覚への刺激によって感じる「状態・感覚」のことを言います。

「状態・感覚」には、物理的なものと、心理的なものの2種類あります。
映像や音声から受ける「刺激」から、首や背骨、頭の中や体全体がぞくぞくすることが物理的な感覚で、幸福感や安らぎ、落ち着き、気持ちの良い眠気などを感じるのが心理的な感覚です。

ASMRの「刺激」を受ける一般的なタイプは、
・視覚（見て）
・聴覚（聞いて）
・触覚（触って）
の３つです。

※)
視覚の例：目を見つめられる、ゆっくりとした手の動きなど
触覚の例：軽いタッチやマッサージ、頭を触れるなど
聴覚の例：人の声(囁き、ゆっくりした声、優しい声)や口の音(咀嚼、呼吸)、物体(タッピング、スクラッチング、操作音、なでる)など様々…

「刺激」を得る場所として、私のチャンネルの動画のような電子の中、もしくは人の声や動作、物の音など実生活の中でも感じることがあります。
直接得る刺激以外でも、想像したり瞑想したり、知らぬ間にASMRが引き起こされる場合もあります。

ASMRの刺激と、引き起こされる感覚は個人間で大きく異なります。
全体に共通して言えるのは、ASMRは多種多様なきっかけにより引き起こされた「深いリラックス状態」であるということ。

音や映像の好み、感じ方は人それぞれですので、ASMRの動画は、好き嫌いが極端に分かれるジャンルかもしれません。
私の動画以外にも、ASMRを引き起こすきっかけになる映像や音声がたくさんありますので、是非ご自身の好きな動画を探してみてくださいね。

※たまに上記ジャンルに関係ない雑談やお知らせ動画も投稿することがございますので、是非タイトルで確認してくださいd(-_^)（ASMR動画は、タイトルにASMRと記載しております。）

※無断転載はご遠慮願います。

Eu comecei tudo isso, com a intenção de fazer pelos outros, aquilo que o asmr sempre fez por mim, ajudar, seja numa noite solitária, seja com a ansiedade, seja por um dia ruim. Eu amo asmr e a capacidade que ele tem de ajudar alguém que precisa, e tento, dia após dia, ajudar quem eu conseguir atravéz dele, e se eu conseguir, serei o cara mais feliz do mundo, por isso, obrigado, de coração, se consegui te ajudar, nem que seja só por 12 minutos, isso me faz feliz❤️

地球には空気が存在していて、その中で複数のものが接している。
それだけで「音」は生まれます。
わたしはその生まれる音に耳をすませ日常の些細な物音を収音しています。
皆さんともいいハーモニーが奏でられるといいなと思っていますよ。
頑張って更新するのでたまには見に来て欲しいです。

This is "Seloli Kawai"  ASMR sound colecter.（Start posting videos in October 2019）
There is air on Earth, and several things touch each other.
Then "sound" is born.
I listen to the sound that is born and pick up the trivial sounds of everyday life.
I hope everyone can play good harmony.
I'll do my best to update it, so I'd like you to come and see it occasionally.

这是ASMR声音顾问的“ Seloli Kawai”。（从2019年10月开始发布视频）
地球上有空气，几件事相互接触。
然后，“声音”诞生了。
我听着出生的声音，拾起日常生活中的琐碎声音。
希望大家能和睦相处。

title: Asmr медитация
description:
Медитация – это психическое упражнение, первоначально возникшее как часть духовно-религиозной практики, которое выполняется, как правило, путем концентрации внимания на одном объекте (чаще всего внутреннем, например на дыхании), либо посредством направления внимания на то, что происходит в данный момент здесь и сейчас (открытое наблюдение), не позволяя человеку застревать в своих мыслях.
Медитация является практическим средством успокоения ума с целью отпустить имеющиеся субъективные предубеждения, основанные на концептуальном мышлении, и увидеть реальность такой, какой она является на самом деле, открыто и ясно.
Meditation is a mental exercise, originally originated as part of a spiritual and religious practice, which is performed, as a rule, by concentrating on one object (most often internal, such as breathing), or by directing attention to what is happening in the moment here and now (open observation), not allowing a person to get stuck in his thoughts.

title: emptiness asmr
description:
"Emptiness” means empty of a separate self. It is full of everything, full of life. The word “emptiness” should not scare us. It is a wonderful word. To be empty does not mean to be nonexistent. If the sheet of paper is not empty, how could the sunshine, the logger, and the forest come into it? How could it be a sheet of paper? The cup, in order to be empty, has to be there. Form, feelings, perceptions, mental formations, and consciousness, in order to be empty of a separate self, have to be there.

Emptiness is the ground of everything. “Thanks to emptiness, everything is possible.” That is a declaration made by Nagarjuna, a Buddhist philosopher of the second century. Emptiness is quite an optimistic concept. If I am not empty, I cannot be here. And if you are not empty, you cannot be there. Because you are there, I can be here. This is the true meaning of emptiness. Form does not have a separate existence.

-Thich Nhat Hanh

title: Relaxing asmr with Flora
description: Peace. Tranquility. relaxation. These are words that come to mind when in the midst of nature. In the go-go-go culture we live in, those sensations can be hard to come by. Listening to nature sounds, such as this recording of a stream, can bring back that feeling of calm. This water sound has many different elements. Closest to the viewer/listener, you can hear the gentle sounds of water lapping. A little further back, you can hear the ambient noise of a stream. In the distance, you can hear the cascading sounds of water flowing over a small waterfall. And deep in the jungle, you hear the sounds of cicadas singing. All of the water sounds together create a relaxing ambience. This water white noise is helpful for blocking out annoying sounds so that you can sleep, study, focus or relax. It'

title: ASMR Eliza
description:
Hi, I'm Eliza and welcome to my ASMR channel!
I post new videos every week :)

Like many people I've experienced ASMR for as long as I can remember without knowing there was a name for it. 

I discovered ASMR on youtube around 5 years ago and since then I have used it almost everyday to help deal with anxiety, stress and trouble sleeping. I hope that my content may be able to help you in the same way that other ASMRtists have helped me. 

My favourite triggers are personal attention, visual triggers and lights, so you can expect to see plenty of those on this channel. 

Thank you for being here! 
Now get comfortable, relax and enjoy :)

title: Asmr Kim8
description:
You can now listen to me on Spotify, Amazon Music, Samsung Podcast, Podcast Index and Listen Notes. Links are in the banner.
Hello my name is Kim. I have been a Holistic Therapist for 20 years. I am now doing more online and offering ASMR to you. I am currently using TikTok for my lives under the name of asmr_kim8 where I go live as often as I can, work permitting.  Headphone's are recommended for the best experience.
"ASMR"  Autonomous Sensory Meridian Response is a relaxing often sedative sensation, that begins on the scalp and moves down the body. Also known as "Brain Massage". it is triggered by placid sights and sounds, such as "Whispering, Accents, and Crackles". It helps with anxiety, insomnia and stress. Hey there! I'm Eddie from Canada! And I do ASMR videos mostly focused on...

- Roleplays
- Soft Spoken and Whispered Video Game Let's Plays
- History and Education
- Relaxing Sound Therapy

But primarily, I just wanna help you fall asleep :)

What the heck is ASMR? It stands for Autonomous Sensory Meridian Response... which really doesn't help explain what it is at all! 

Essentially, it's a relaxing tingling sensation some people get that starts in your scalp and can work it's way down your back. It's usually triggered by external stimuli such as when you go for a haircut, or have an eye exam, or watch someone concentrate on a task. I remember getting it as a child when my friends would trace letters and words on my back and I had to guess what they wrote.

Not everyone gets ASMR tingles, but the videos can be used for relaxation and to help shut your brain off at night.

title: Bryoni ASMR
description:
Hey there, I'm Bryoni. 
ASMR is an abbreviation for Autonomous Sensory Meridian Response. It is a response or reaction to a certain sound, visual, or stimuli. ASMR can help individuals to reduce depression, insomnia, and anxiety. Alternatively, it can be used to help with relaxation for sleep and as a mechanism to help with studying. 

**DISCLAIMER** 
I create ASMR videos with the intention of helping people to relax, un-wind, and sleep. ASMR can be used as an aid to assist with relaxation, studying, and de-stressing. You should seek professional help if you are struggling with your mental health. ASMR is by no means a viable treatment.

title: Max's ASMR
description:
ASMR I create it for fun


goals:
5,000 subs
10,000 subs
it stand for?
ASMR is the term for the sensation people get when they watch stimulating videos or take part in other activities — usually ones that involve personal attention. Many people describe the feeling as “tingles” that run through the back of someone’s head and spine. Others say the feeling is deeply relaxing, and can even cause them to fall asleep.


How does it work?
How ASMR works varies greatly from person to person. Some — perhaps most — people don’t get it at all. And the science on ASMR is basically nonexistent, so our understanding of it is so far based on anecdotes from around the internet.

What is ASMR?

Autonomous sensory meridian response (ASMR), sometimes auto sensory meridian response, is a tingling sensation that typically begins on the scalp and moves down the back of the neck and upper spine. A pleasant form of paresthesia, it has been compared with auditory-tactile synesthesia and may overlap with frisson.

title: LeanFan ASMR
description:
Hi Guys! My name is Helena and I am glad to see you on my ASMR channel! :)
ASMR stands for the autonomous sensory response of the meridian, which can be felt like a tingling sensation on the skin, which usually begins on the scalp and descends to the back of the neck and upper spine.
I hope my videos help you relax, fall asleep, or make you hungry (^_^)
_____________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

Привет Ребята! Меня зовут Лена и я рада видеть вас на своем АСМР канале! :)
ASMR обозначает автономный сенсорный ответ меридиональной реакции, которая может ощущаться как покалывание на коже, которое обычно начинается на коже головы и опускается к задней части шеи и верхней части позвоночника.
Я надеюсь мои видео помогут вам расслабиться, уснуть или же заставят вас проголодаться (^_^)
